description:
Cyber Neon Bundle is a collection of two cyber theme games; CYBERHUNT and RAZORTRON 2000. Both are frenetic action games where youâ€™ll use your skills to win everything! 

CYBERHUNT is a retro procedurally generated twin stick shooter that takes you back to the sweet to the sweet arcade machines era, where you can play the arcade and missions mode.

RAZORTRON 2000 is a retro top-down endless racing game, where the player will try to beat the highscore, unlock new cars and climb your way to the top of the leaderboards on this love letter to coin eater arcade machines era!	

Bundle Features
- Two games to choose;
- Both games with beautiful retro pixel art with aesthetics vibe;
- Frenetic Music; 
- Many unlockables in both games;
